3. M: You probably check this from time to time while 
you’re watching a sports game such as baseball, 
basketball, or football. By seeing this, you can see 
how the match is going. This also shows playing 
time and other relevant facts and figures, such as 
the count of balls and strikes on a baseball batter. 
In the past, a mechanical clock and numeral cards 
were used. So, when a point was made, a person 
would put the appropriate cards on a hook. These 
days, electronic devices are used for this, and the 
person who operates this uses a control panel.
