announced the list of nominated films for this 
year. The list consists of five films for each 
category. This year, for the first time, five 
hundred non­professionals will be allowed to 
participate in the selection process. Anyone who is 
interested can apply. If you become a judge, you 
will watch the films on the list at the designated 
theaters and select winners by online vote. The 
application deadline is October 16, 2008. We hope 
many of you will participate.
